{"tid":322552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總辭就係將香港變成深圳同燃盡香港最後國際地位","createTime":"2017-07-15T02:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T02:23:42.000Z","uid":22054,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3df05081045eb09ff6fa16af38135f130e17099","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:21:58.000Z","msg":"總辭後成立國民議會，廣場制憲，同時要求美國取消香港關係法，如果美國同中國唔置在，香港人又唔理咪開開心心齊齊做蚛蟈人，如果國際社會都想繼續借香港洗黑錢就會逼中國承認國民議會地位及新憲法變相重奪議會甚至獨立<br />\n<br />\n總辭，就係將香港所有國際地位用黎做一次豪賭，贏就贏盡，輸都輸盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d054cc8b25859ad9c69806b8eaf7f1471f0347e","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02589dc0a38920a53fec715a5618fcda2cede5b5","tid":322552,"uid":33797,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"飯氓鬼同你玩，講民主都係為咗呃飯食咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a865674f350e84b5b94a1e1a4be9518650b26634","tid":322552,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"香港會變成第二個上海"},{"pid":"b8114aa23e5aa869611ee504da3cdf200ba1b7ca","tid":322552,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦 而家都係抱住攬炒心態<br />\n<br />\n共產黨萬歲！🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳😍"},{"pid":"c45f9252fcdf9763d5cf3612f58de23d67081568","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港會變成第二個上海</blockquote><br />\n香港點都會變香港市，只係有得賭而一舖輸清袋定係咬穀種咬到破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d417c2482289f79659263f3bc4832d2471ca664","tid":322552,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"到今日香港仲有野可以輸咩 遲早都會變第二個深圳 不如賭一鋪好過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但飯民仲要呃飯食 點會總辭"},{"pid":"87c52a5fca2a4ccf11618ebace8861e97017657d","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"總辭後有冇然後？贏盡同輸盡都冇然後，曬冷一係佢破產一係自己破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017f886f0b2a550dc04b60cbd9f4de55f881ff11","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009643ac062557440a34cad5eea62c0de4630d1b","tid":322552,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e6b9a43f357b38094ec923c3d73105e71dcbbfa","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cfca6ae33638918f2f505d6f3d53bc953c8554","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1985145f020880ace38961fc6485d6f50a8d0c8","tid":322552,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"輸撚硬都得"},{"pid":"49a8ecb96e6e974751119bc03a0e7779770ba0bf","tid":322552,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf534bdc8343bc3bae016b7c26d47f9dd6abe6e9","tid":322552,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輸撚硬都得</blockquote><br />\n事實就係你輸到破產又係破產，食殻種食到破產都係破產，壞掂都係破，不如自己輸曬賴自己on9好過死左都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d630cdfa5d160ddaf7887a730724221f268eb6b7","tid":322552,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201